name: ONE EVO AIR SUIT
description:
ONE EVO AIR SUIT
The ONE EVO AIR Suit combines the most advanced materials with an ergonomic cut to improve ventilation and driver freedom of movement. With pre-shaped sleeves, elastic inserts, and a 10% increase in breathability, it reduces fatigue while maintaining FIA safety compliance.

• OMP Air technology
• FIA 8856-2018 (SFI upon request)
• 10% more breathable and 7% lighter than current ONE EVO X SUIT
• Pre-shaped sleeves and legs to improve ergonomic fit
• X-shaped elastic inserts at the knees
• Soft hand feel with white or black inner lining depending on suit color
• Extremely refined finish with differentiated threads and new cuffs
• Shaped collar
• Extraction handles
• Stretch insert on back, crotch and armhole
• Ultraflat seams
• Premium metal zip
• Hidden outer pocket
• OMP branded velcro at collar closure

Supports race endurance by maintaining comfort and temperature regulation over long sessions.

Colors :Black/Medium grey (071), Navy blue/Cool blue (244), Iron grey/Fluo yellow (178), Medium grey/Black (282), Silver/Iron Grey (283)
Sizes :46÷64

name: ONE-S AIR SUIT
description:
ONE-S AIR SUIT
Designed for highest lightness and ease of customization, the ONE-S AIR Suit features an ultralightweight, breathable fabric and simplified cut. It’s ideal for teams seeking branding flexibility without sacrificing fit or comfort.

• OMP Air technology
• FIA 8856-2018 (SFI upon request)
• 10% more breathable and 18% lighter than previous ONE-S
• Minimal cut design studied to optimize customization
• Pre-shaped sleeves to improve ergonomic fit
• Elastic inserts on back,crotch and armhole
• Soft hand feel with optional black inner lining
• Extremely refined finish with differentiated threads and minimal cuffs
• Shaped collar
• Extraction handles
• Ultraflat seams
• Premium metal zip
• Hidden outer pocket
• OMP branded velcro at collar closure
Built to improve driver's focus through increased freedom of movement and reduced thermal load.

Colors :Black/White/Silver (171), Silver/Black (189), Navy blue/Fluo orange (249), Red/White (063), Black/Teal (379)
Sizes :46÷64

name: ONE ART AIR SUIT
description:
ONE ART AIR SUIT
Based on new revolutionary OMP Air technology, the ONE ART AIR Suit is built for drivers who require extreme breathability and complete design flexibility. Made with a wide-weave fire-retardant fabric and polyester blend, it supports temperature control without compromising protection. This suit enables full customization using OMP’s sublimation-ready OMP Art technology.

• OMP Air technology
• FIA 8856-2018 approved
• Over 40% more breathable and 12% lighter than previous ONE ART compound
• Extremely refined finish with differentiated threads
• Newly designed cuffs
• White inner lining (optional black)
• Unlimited customization thanks to the totally printable fabric (OMP Art technology)
• Shaped collar
• Extraction handles
• Stretch insert on back, crotch and armhole
• Ultraflat seams
• Premium metal zip
• Hidden outer pocket
• OMP branded velcro at collar closure
Engineered to maintain thermal stability and optimize fit, the ONE ART AIR Suit supports focus in high-temperature racing environments.

name: ONE-S Suit
description:
ONE-S Suit
Fire retardant top level overall. Developed for the highest lightness without sacrificing the comfort. Semi floating arm bellows, legs and inner collar inserts in soft knitted elastic fabric. Breathable and elastic inserts in new strecth Dry System fabric on lumbs. High breathability parts in Dry System 3D material on low back, hips, neck and under the sleeves. Regular fit, with ultraflat antirubbing seams, soft knitted inside and a comfortable hidden inner pocket. With belt to improve fitting. 

Colours: Black (071),Silver (083), Navy blue/fluo orange (249)
Sizes: 46-64
Homologation: FIA 8856-2018

name: TECNICA SuperLight
description:
TECNICA SuperLight
Fireproof high level overall, developed with high performance lightweight materials

- Bielastic inserts to facilitate an ergonomic fitting, breathable inserts at sides and underarms to give the best comfort
- Ultraflat antirubbing seams, fishbone outside top stitching
- 2L inner compound made of a soft knitted fabric quilted with meta-aramid non woven fabric
- Contrast color details such as pockets profile and inner collar plus edge

Colors: Black/Silver (171), White/Anthracite (373), Navy blue/orange (249), Green/fluo yellow (031)
Sizes: 46-64
Homologation: FIA 8556-2018

name: TECNICA EVO Suit
description:
TECNICA EVO Suit
Professional fire retardant suit featured by high-level fabrics. Floating arms with elastic bellows to increase freedom of movement, breathable fabric inserts to give the best comfort. Ultraflat antirubbing seams, inner fabric made in soft knitted fabric and practical front pocket on right side. "Fishbone" quilting, fresh and aggressive design. 

Colors: Black/red (073), Black/white (076), White/anthracite (373), Black/anthracite/fluo yellow (178), Navy blue/white/grey/cyan (246), Royal blue/fluo yellow (044)
Sizes: 44-64
Homologation: FIA 8556-2018

name: TECNICA Hybrid Suit
description:
TECNICA Hybrid Suit
Professional racing suit make use of traditional Nomex fabrics mixed with high technology printed inserts and high quality embroidered details.
Floating sleeves with elastic bellow, knitted elastic insert on the back for maximum freedom of movement. Shaped collar with inner soft knitted fabric, adjustable velcro's belt, ultra-flat anti-rubbing seams and soft insert on groin guarantee maximum comfort.
Breathable inserts on hips and under the sleeves, pockets with diagonal cut on front, fishbone quilting.

Colors: Black/silver (171), Black/fluo yellow (178), Navy blue/cyan (244), Red/black (060), Silver/black (089)
Sizes: 44-64
Homologation: FIA 8556-2018

name: KS-X Art Suit
description:
KS-X Art Suit
Top level ultra light and totally printed karting suit. Developed with the most important karting teams and drivers. Without seams on waist and lateral seams moved on front to increase driver's comfort whilst on the karting seat. Ultrasoft resistant fabrics, elastics insert on groin, underfoot retainer, protective and comfortable padding on knees, high breathability inserts under the sleeves, low cut neck. Floating arms with elastic bellow, stretch insert on back. Unlimited customization ways. 
FIA 8877-2022 HOMOLOGATION.

Colors: Black/yellow/red (378)
Adult sizes: 44-62 (KA0-1731-A01)

name: KS-4 SUIT my2026
description:
KS-4 SUIT my2026
The KS-4 suit balances function and style with a lightweight construction, breathable zones, and contrast piping. Designed for karting sessions where heat management and comfort directly impact focus.

• Durable external polyester fabric
• Inner ultra breathable net lyning 
• Design with contrast stripes and piping
• Laser cut micro holes located on strategical areas for improved breathability and temperature control (AirFlow System)
• Floating arms
• Elastic band on back with strech insert to guarantee best comfort and fitting
• Inner soft collar lyning
• New wrist two-tone cuff to improve fit
• OMP branded puller on autolock zipper
• Available in adult and kids sizes
• Adjustable belt at waist
• Two pockets at sides
Built for ventilation and mobility, this suit supports endurance during high-intensity karting use.

Colors :Black/Red (073), Red (061), Anthracite/Fluo yellow (184), Blue (041)
Sizes :S÷XXL

Ultra comfortable mechanic's overall made in stretch 4-way fabric. The new generation ultralightweight material water resistant, breathable and windproof guarantees a next-level of comfort and freedom of movement. Removable shapedknee pads in EVA. name: BLAST EVO
description:

The knitted elastic fabric inserts on back and hips and the comfortable arm-bellows guarantee the best freedom of movements. description:
KS-1 PRO Body Protection 
FIA homologated karting body protection. Outside in resistant polycarbonate material, inner lining in nitrile rubber and shockproof memory foam that dissipates energy in case of accident. KS-1 PRO offers complete protection to the driver (ribs, front and back) combined with maximum comfort thanks to the internal padding and the exclusive auto-adjustable fitting system. Adjustable shoulder and lateral straps with velcro, shaped front shield to get best comfort and higher protection.
 
KS-1 PRO can accommodate various heights and body shapes thanks to seven different sizes: four standard-fit sizes (S-M-L-XL) and 3 wide-fit sizes (M wide, L wide, XL wide).
The spare inner padding kit (6mm thicker) guarantees a perfect fit also to skinniest bodies without compromising comfort and safety (available as optional sold separately, easy to set up thanks to velcro quick attachments - part n° KK049/PAD).

name: HGT EVO SEAT
description:
HGT EVO SEAT
The HGT EVO Fiberglass Seat is designed for GT cars, offering a strong and versatile solution for a wide range of drivers. Its fiberglass shell combines durability with a controlled weight balance, while the wide internal shape ensures comfort across different body types. Wide shoulder and head support improve lateral stability, providing consistent safety and focus in demanding driving conditions.

• FIA 8855-2021 homologated
• Wide internal seat shape for versatile driver fit
• Extended shoulder and head support for stability
• Designed specifically for GT applications
• Two different homologated side brackets available for adaptable installation
• Shell weight 12.8 Kg

This seat balances safety, fit, and adaptability, ensuring drivers remain stable and supported throughout competition use.

name: ONE-D 2" Pull Down
description:
ONE-D 2" Pull Down
Ultralightweight and comfortable safety harness for saloon cars in Dyneema®, the strongest fiber in the world™. Forged aluminium ultralight adjusters, buckle in ergal machined from solid and magnesium. The Harness ensures best safety level ever thanks to the ultra-resistant buckle with an anti-unwitting opening system and exclusive double pin T-bar crotch attachments. Adjustable setting of shoulder and lap straps with exclusive F1-inspired “double fold” system for a practical and strong hold. FHR only.

ALSO AVAILABLE IN MAGNESIUM-FREE VERSION UPON REQUEST (DA0102BHSL)

Straps and attachments:
Shoulders: 2" roll bar, Lap: 2" pull down carabiner, Crotch: 2" snap hook

Color: Black/white
Points: 6
Homologation: FIA 8853-2016

name: FIA 8865-2015 ECU - Standard configuration
description:
FIA 8865-2015 ECU - Standard configuration
Electronic control unit for FIA 8865-2015 fire extinguisher systems

• ECU with switch & LEDs on the top cover of the ECU
• Two-ways cable to connect activation buttons and bottle to the ECU
• Waterproof dedicated cables and connectors
• Customizable cable extensions
• Internal/External activation button
• Possibility to add extra activation button
• Easy battery replacement
• IP65/67 certified

Also available in CANBUS version upon request to connect the ECU to the CANBUS line of the car. The CANBUS interface can be customized to fullfill the team’s/driver’s requests. All the ECU versions, can have different front and back panels, depending on the position in the cockpit.

name: FIA 8865-2015 ECU - Remote switch&leds configuration
description:
FIA 8865-2015 ECU - Remote switch&leds configuration
Remote electronic control unit for FIA 8865-2015 fire extinguisher systems

• Test/Armed Switch & LEDs on a dedicated panel that can be placed everywhere in the cockpit
• Three-ways cable to connect switch & LEDs, activation buttons and bottle to the ECU
• Optimal solution for small cockpit
• Possibility to add extra activation button
• Easy battery replacement
• Customizable cable extensions

Also available in CANBUS version upon request to connect the ECU to the CANBUS line of the car. The CANBUS interface can be customized to fullfill the team’s/driver’s requests. All the ECU versions, can have different front and back panels, depending on the position in the cockpit.

name: GP-R Helmet
description:
GP-R Helmet 
Full face helmet in composite material. Lightweight shell, high ventilation thanks to four air intakes on chin and eight vents on top. The standard sized eyeport allows to use the helmet with both classic shields and touring sun peak (sold separately - SC179) and makes the helmet suitable for several motorsports disciplines, from formula cars to GT cars. Soft inner comfortable fabrics allows best fitting comfort; double ring closure. Hans posts fitted. 
Spare parts: Clear visor SC195, Dark visor SC196, Iridium visor SC197, Pivot kit SC194

Color: White (020)
Sizes: XXS (54-55), XS (55-56), S (57-58), M (58-59), L (60-61), XL(61-61+)
Homologation: FIA 8859-2015

name: GP-R K Helmet
description:
GP-R K Helmet 
Full face karting helmet in composite material. Lightweight shell, high ventilation thanks to four air intakes on chin and eight vents on top. Standard size eyeport, soft inner comfortable fabrics that allows best fitting comfort; double ring closure. 
Spare parts: Clear visor SC195, Dark visor SC196, Iridium visor SC197, Pivot kit SC194

Color: White (020)
Sizes: XXS (54-55), XS (55-56), S (57-58), M (58-59), L (60-61), XL(61-61+)
Homologation: SNELL K2020

name: KJ-8 EVO
description:
KJ-8 EVO
Full face karting CMR helmet made in composite material. Lightweight, with soft and comfortable high breathability internal lining, bordered strap with double ring clousure and high precision adjustable visor with easy block system. The air vents and intakes ensure the best air ducting. Spare iridium blue visor included in the box.

Color: White (020)
Sizes: XS-L
Homologation: CMR 2016

name: Circuit EVO2
description:
Circuit EVO2
Full face thermoplastic helmet with breathable and comfortable lining (not fire retardant), removable cheek pads, chin curtain and removable breath guard. Micrometric quick release padded strap, anti scratch step setting visor. Aerodynamic lines, adjustable air vents. Available in classic colors or in modern bright fluo yellow.
ECE 22.06 HOMOLOGATED.

Spare parts and accessories:
Clear visor (SC0-0198), Dark visor (SC0-0199), Spare visor pivot kit (SC0-0200), Spare front top air vents (SC0-0201), Spare chin air vent (SC0-0202)

Colors: White (020), Matte black (170), Fluo yellow (099)
Sizes: XS-XXL
Homologation: ECE 22.06

name: J-Rally Helmet
description:
J-Rally Helmet 
Open face racing helmet. High quality lightweight composite material shell, high breathability fire retardant internal lining. Complete with an anti dazzle peak fitted with a tinted visor strip. With Hans posts fitted. 

Pre-installed ZeroNoise intercom kit (ultra-thin loudspeaker integrated and adjustable microphone boom) with female Nexus plug. 

Color: White (020)
Sizes: S (57-58), M (58-59), L (60-61), XL(61-62)
Homologation: FIA 8859-2024

ECE 22.06 HOMOLOGATED.

name: CO-DRIVER BAG
description:
CO-DRIVER BAG
Designed with input from WRC co-drivers, this storage solution supports rapid access and organization under race conditions. Built for durability, with multiple attachment and storage configurations.

• Designed with feedback from WRC co-drivers
• Velcro loops on the back for roll cage attachment
• Double frontal zip for secure closure
• Multiple pockets and compartments for organizing pens, documents, and accessories
• Compact and functional design
• OMP logo on front pocket

Improves operational readiness by reducing search time and supporting route preparation.

name: GS Chair
description:
GS Chair
Wheeled office chair upholstered in vinyl with high quality reclining mechanism, hydraulic seat height adjustment and removable 3-way adjustable armrests. The seat is manufactured with the best quality components available, from the movement elements to the plastic parts. Aluminium base, racing-inspired design with 3D effect sewing.
The ergonomic high-comfort shape and EN1335 homologation make the chair perfect for your office, at home or in the paddock.

Colors: Black vinyl (071), Black/yellow vinyl (178), Black/red vinyl (073), Black vinyl with breathable Airnet fabric (276)
Homologation: EN1335

name: GSX Chair
description:
GSX Chair
Wheeled gaming chair upholstered in vinyl with high quality reclining mechanism, hydraulic seat height adjustment and removable 4-way full adjustable armrests. The seat is manufactured with the best quality components available, from the movement elements to the plastic parts. Racing-inspired design with upholstering with 3D effect sewing, racing-spring on piston, colored inserts on wheels and base.
The ergonomic high-comfort shape and EN1335 homologation make the chair perfect for your office, at home or in the paddock.

Colors: Black vinyl (071), Black/fluo yellow vinyl (178), Black/fluo green vinyl (274), Black/fluo orange vinyl (179)
Homologation: EN1335
